channel.title: Moparscape installed, waiting for downloading file..?
channel.description: Okay.. it's taken me forever to get Moparscape installed. Now that it is, I am on the loading screen, and it says "Downloading Files" and the percent.. why is it taking tons and tons of time to do this? I remember when I had it on my old computer, I could get onto the login screen way more quickly. My internet isn't slow at all.
